executableContent.instructions:
Finally, you'll see what CSS can do for your project. We'll begin to cover CSS soon, but for now, you'll only need to paste CSS into a blank stylesheet here in the project. There are no tests, but you'll see a lot of changes in the appearance of the blog.

1. Paste the code block we give you below into `style.css`.
2. View the changes by clicking Run Code.

```CSS
body {
 background-color: #F5F5F5;
 text-align: center;
}

h2 {
 color: #555050; 
 text-decoration: underline;
}

img {
 width: 150px;
 border: solid #ece4e9 4px;
 border-radius: 15px;
}
```

